question: Nang taun pira 'net interest income excluding cib markets' paling dhuwur?
Pira total Pendapatan Bunga Bersih Pasar CIB, ing yuta, saka 2014 nganti 2016?
Taun 2015, pinten net interest yield segmen sing aset bunga rata-rata paling sithik?
Jelasna tren 'net interest yield on average interest-earning assets excluding cib markets' saka 2014 nganti 2016.
answer: Net interest yield on average interest-earning assets excluding CIB markets sepisan mudun saka 2,53% ing 2014 dadi 2,49% ing 2015, banjur mundhak signifikan dadi 2,59% ing 2016, pungkasane periode ing titik paling dhuwur.

question: Sebutna taun-taun ing ngendi total 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' luwih saka $45.000 yuta.
Taun 2016, pira persene 'average cib markets interest-earning assets' saka total 'average interest-earning assets'?

Yen Net Interest Income iku saka Net Interest Yield dikalikan Average Interest-Earning Assets, pira kira-kira 'cib markets net interest income' ing taun 2014 yen yield-ne 1.25 tinimbang 1.15? (Kabeh nilai ing yuta)
Jelasna gegayutan antarane pertumbuhan total 'rata-rata aset sing ngasilake bunga' lan owah-owahan ing 'net interest yield on average interest-earning assets 2013 managed basis' sajrone telung taun.
answer: Ora ana korelasi langsung sing konsisten. Saka taun 2014 nganti 2015, total rata-rata aset sing ngasilake bunga saya gedhe nalika net interest yield mudhun. Nanging, saka taun 2015 nganti 2016, aset lan yield mundhak. Gegayutan sing ora ajeg iki nuduhake yen faktor liyane kajaba jumlah aset total nduweni pengaruh gedhe marang net interest yield.

question: Ana pira item ing tabel sing diterangake kanthi gamblang minangka pangurangan saka total sadurunge, adhedhasar deskripsi?
answer: less : cib markets net interest income ( c )
less : average cib markets interest-earning assets ( c )

question: Taun pira sing nuduhake owah-owahan persentase taun-liyan taun sing paling gedhe (positif utawa negatif) ing 'cib markets net interest income'?
Taun pira sing ngasilake bathi bunga paling akeh?
